#. Tag: para
#: ay_bigfile.xml:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "A lot of major changes were introduced with &productname; &productnumber; (the switch to systemd and &grub; for example). These changes also required fundamental changes in &ay;, therefore you cannot use &ay; control files created on previous &productname; versions to install &productname; &productnumber; and vice versa."
