#. Tag: #text
#: ay_bigfile.xml:15055
#, no-c-format
msgid "You might expect the control file to contain 3 partitions. This is not the case. You will end up with two partitions and the first partition is a mix up of the swap and the root partition. Settings configured in both partitions, like"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: #text
#: ay_bigfile.xml:15058
#, no-c-format
msgid ", will be used from the second file. Settings that only exist in the first or second partition, will be copied to the merged partition too."
