#. Tag: para
#: ay_bigfile.xml:16011
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you choose to pass information to linuxrc using the <filename>info</filename> file, it is possible to integrate the keywords in the XML control file. In this case the file needs to be accessible to linuxrc and needs to be named <filename>info</filename> ."
