#. Tag: para
#: ay_bigfile.xml:16017
#, no-c-format
msgid "Linuxrc will look for a string ( <literal>start_linuxrc_conf</literal> in the control file which represents the beginning of the file. If it is found, it will parse the content starting from that string and will finish when the string <literal>end_linuxrc_conf</literal> is found. The options are stored in the control file in the following way:"
